<p itemprop="description"><b>创作立场声明：</b>本人原创，转载注明出处，严禁盗图，违都依法依规追究责任</p><p itemprop="description">今天介绍的这个案例属于北京业主，精装四居</p><p itemprop="description">黄铜色装饰吊顶、踢脚线+原木地板，原装修自带轻奢感</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813750f9279727.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">19年末沟通定制</p><p itemprop="description">因为疫情和宝宝降生，业主一家生活状态发生很大改变</p><p itemprop="description">也彻底改变了业主的定制规划</p><h2 id="cl_0">业主说</h2><p itemprop="description">因疫情宅在家，所以有更多时间重新梳理定制需求。</p><h3>孩子还小，需要留出活动空间，原来规划的一些家具取消了，更加注重家具的功能区布置、尺寸规划和“大方且耐看”的风格上。</h3><p itemprop="description">装修嘛，留下一些余地最好，以后还可以慢慢按需添加。</p><p itemprop="description">.</p><p itemprop="description">.</p><p itemprop="description">.</p><p itemprop="description">这是家具布置图</p><p itemprop="description">儿童房因孩子太小暂未订制</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd8137510f571562.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_1">#01“主卧里的mini衣帽间”</h2><p itemprop="description">.</p><p itemprop="description">每个女主的梦想家都有衣帽间，所以业主花了超多心思打造了这个mini衣帽间</p><p itemprop="description">这个主卧的面积约15m²，原本这里有一个开发商赠送的衣帽间</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813752b2c28825.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">但业主觉得板材的不环保、显廉价<br/></p><p itemprop="description">且功能很不实用，就给拆了</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813752e32e9839.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">重新设计时，业主希望可以挂衣、收包、藏鞋<br/></p><p itemprop="description">还要能放两个28寸旅行箱</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd813752d13a3735.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">为此讨论修改过很多次内部结构</p><p itemprop="description">最终设计分区合理，还装了灯带</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813757428e9446.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813758a488853.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">安装完成的衣帽间呈L型<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81375bce40805.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">白橡木做美式风格其实也很好看</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81375dd53f9944.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">衣帽间当然少不了落地试衣镜</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81375cd0f13983.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">站在这里，可以默默欣赏自己的美貌，哈哈</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137604de91201.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">右侧柜有两个明抽屉，放置小件衣物，方便拿取</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813762c1479443.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">为了抽屉和正面衣柜门不会互相影响，左侧柜门采用了推拉门设计</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813763f73a9278.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">衣帽间柜子背板正对着卧室，工厂按流云衣柜面板标准精心选料，即便背板也要颜值在线</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81376545b06383.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">宝宝出生后卧室加了张婴儿陪伴床，<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/shuzhuangtai/" target="_blank">梳妆台</a>和<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/chuangtougui/" target="_blank">床头柜</a>暂时取消</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137665e3e120.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">紧挨着的大床也是特别定制</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81376899617541.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">业主喜欢梳背床头，又希望能储物且视觉轻盈</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_18/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81376af5931953.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">于是有了梳背架式床及悬浮箱体床的结合体<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_19/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81376d2c0c5130.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_2">#02“L形转角玄关柜”</h2><p itemprop="description">..</p><p itemprop="description">退回玄关，入户位置只有个L形小转角墙体，略显鸡肋，不好利用</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_20/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137706fcd2916.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">玄关柜如何设计？设计师用了很多心思，开始是这样<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_21/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137737e6f2807.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">功能虽有却遮挡餐厅采光，视觉不清爽，经过多轮沟通，最终决定将柜子“内折”，柜体变成三边围绕转角的L型</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_22/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81377572c7622.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这是设计图<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_23/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81377424144758.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">设计心思很巧妙，师傅表示安装难度有点高<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_24/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813774622a4137.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">进门位置看，柜体轻薄，视觉轻盈</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137769e472240.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">门卡钥匙包包小物随手放<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_26/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd81377d01a04200.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">进出门衣服随手挂</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_27/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81377d1ef3916.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">转着圈看各方向一体性都超强<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81377dd32e2226.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_29/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81377ce8f3280.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_3">#03“多功能宽敞客餐厅”</h2><h2 id="cl_4">.</h2><h2 id="cl_5">.</h2><p itemprop="description">业主强调公共空间家具设计要轻量化，先说客厅</p><p itemprop="description">这是原本家具布置图，为给孩子更宽阔活动空间取消了茶几</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_30/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137826ccd5288.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">中间空地儿是亲子互动区、瑜伽区<br/></p><p itemprop="description">进门第一感受就是：客厅好宽敞</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_31/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378308924944.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">五斗柜+<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/dianshigui/" target="_blank">电视柜</a>+展示柜+储物柜，整排简美组合电视柜，搞定就近收纳</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_32/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378597165105.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">因错落有致，不会显压抑和拥挤<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_33/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813789785c43.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_34/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd813787a1ad5721.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">全部采用高腿设计，一体性强且方便<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/saodijiqiren/" target="_blank">扫地机器人</a>进出</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_35/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813788ded68804.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_36/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378b4fce8348.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">业主自己搭配了类色系沙发和窗帘<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_37/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378e28cb8590.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">玄关右侧是餐厅<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_38/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd81378e280f5457.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">以大桌为中心，业主希望这里也能成为多功能区</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_39/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378e2d45469.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">日常聚餐，家庭会议，做手工搭乐高，可以自由切换定位</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_40/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137947dc59701.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_41/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813793d44f8582.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">订制的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/canbiangui/" target="_blank">餐边柜</a>上下安装长虹玻璃<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_42/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81379597e81700.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">视觉轻盈，颜值在线</p><p itemprop="description">储物、展示、操作台都有了</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_43/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137967d294437.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">金属细腿和家里金色踢脚线非常搭</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_44/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813796b0773132.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_6">#04“简美小书房”</h2><p itemprop="description">.</p><p itemprop="description">书房面积较小，书柜书桌相对而放</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_45/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813799139d32.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">书柜选择的简美风格，【尺寸 / 长1.9m*高2.48m*进深0.37m】</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_46/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81379e13134345.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_47/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137a0704e441.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">上面展示下面储物，中间配置两个超大抽屉</p><p