<p itemprop="description"><span style="line-height: 0; font-size: 14px;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 14px;"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 14px; line-height: 0;">﻿</span>冬日对于哥特最重要的是什么？</span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">线索</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">1:</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">身处北方的冬日</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;"> </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">气温已经到了零下</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">10</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">  </span></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">线索</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">2:</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">作为中青年</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;"> </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">一般都会放在包中</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;"> </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">随身携带</span></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">线索</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">3:</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">一天之内除了手机</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;"> </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">它的使用频次很高</span></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 14px;">你们猜到是什么了吗？</span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">哥特先公布我的答案就是：随身<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/baowenbaolengbei/" target="_blank">保温杯</a></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;"> </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">你猜对了吗？作为北方人，寒冷的冬日除了必要的保暖物品外，保温杯基本属于公文包中必要的存在</span></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">而作为科技</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">up</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">主，我怎么能使用普普通通的保温杯呢？</span></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-le